Builds the filtered iterator.

This constructor takes a WarcRecord (or a GZWarcRecord if the stream contains compressed records) that will be reused (and thus modified) by calls to hasNext() and next().

Parameters:
in - the input stream.
record - the record used for reading.
filter - the filter.
pl - a (pre-initialized) ProgressLogger that will be updated during reads.
